  <num>32-704</num>
  <heading>Domestic partnership benefits.</heading>
  <text>All health care facilities, including hospitals, convalescent facilities, or other long term care facilities, shall allow a patient’s family member as defined in <cite path="§32-701|(7)">§ 32-701(7)</cite> to visit the patient.</text>
